{"tid":1650594,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發！！】1014人權法集氣會出左不反對通知書","createTime":"2019-10-13T04:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T10:06:19.000Z","uid":264429,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"4f7df7ba55fa904cd0eacb70628da4553ba181b0","tid":1650594,"uid":264429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yxv6ayJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyxv6ayJ.jpg&h=20a0369a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZGjbmFp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZGjbmFp.jpg&h=8f60fd60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/skBhhdL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FskBhhdL.jpg&h=a1485a27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fDzntkr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfDzntkr.jpg&h=5fabf3a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SxGAOks.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSxGAOks.jpg&h=2e46b800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國會預計當地時間星期二審議《香港人權與民主法案》。市民將於本地時間星期一晚七時正在遮打花園舉行集會，以和平、理性、優雅方式促請美國盡快通過法案。集會預計約二千人參與。<br />\n<br />\n警方已就上述集會發出不反對通知書。這是《禁止蒙面規例》生效後首個與反送中相關的合法集會。<br />\n<br />\n在星期六與警方會面時，警方提醒主辦方，須呼籲糾察和參與者在集會時不要蒙面。主辦方將會提醒集會人士有關法例要求和風險，但亦希望即使有人在和平集會期間戴口罩，警方亦不要貿然進入集會場地內執法，引起恐慌。<br />\n<br />\n主辦方呼籲，集會人士採用港鐵以外的交通工具前往和離開遮打花園，並提早規劃行程，以保障安全。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4XhwmFG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4XhwmFG.jpg&h=e7c3f854&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c3a8f768f620011b89863b7c0e9e7f8e2f94341","tid":1650594,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:54:14.000Z","msg":"Good"},{"pid":"8f86f53d537b93d3c6645619a2666b2595406376","tid":1650594,"uid":261558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-1