rc=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148014ef8dc42d0f4356985cb0a786f75f233f02","tid":1650594,"uid":62402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:59:53.000Z","msg":"集會戴口罩會唔會有藉口俾人拉？"},{"pid":"07241ca0c16d8b81288d94b3f2b9f3fe08c8d920","tid":1650594,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:00:28.000Z","msg":"大家可以用下twitter help 去每日領任務retweet！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGZNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=fd5aa62b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKHAaEE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKHAaEE.png&h=6b504c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只要輸入 /task2 就可以知道外國議員外媒名人出左咩重要tweet，大家去retweet啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v8KyGMc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv8KyGMc.png&h=aeb55a2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n做完task2，繼續做埋task1<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntask1係普通帳號但都係重要的tweets!<br />\n求retweet!!!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oySTGM6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoySTGM6.png&h=5c90755c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而task3就係唔直接關香港事，但係同中國人權問題/支爆問題有關的tweets! 歡迎大家去煲大淋火水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vz2Xo1f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvz2Xo1f.png&h=8f68e83d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家響美國過人權法案的時候，<br />\n千祈唔好放棄twitter戰線呀！<br />\n仲有英國話今日會講英女王會講英國版magnitsky Act！<br />\n依家係重要關頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定要一人一twitter!!!!!!<br />\n一路retweet一路去集會！"},{"pid":"ba2bae4e34e9b39c90fcdd490ace54aeb519915f","tid":1650594,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:06:53.000Z","msg":"今晚好唔好一齊請求：<br />\n1.將全體香港警察(包括：文職同學警)及其家屬加入制裁名單<br />\n2.動用全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法<br />\n3.美國遊說自由世界全體國家，嚴格審查有關香港警察及其家屬既移民或居留權申請<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e46e7c352107ee63d69f50eba0bf99f08b0e3287","tid":1650594,"uid":12791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:22:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7f1689be596ca4fbae7bed2330b124b56ab9667b","tid":1650594,"uid":2676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:56:20.000Z","msg":"屌，推返上去啦"},{"pid":"022e162a46f2289f5272d0c6cbb239d0a3ea9421","tid":1650594,"uid":99505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:56:59.000Z","msg":"去"},{"pid":"ddf80757f7b41dfcb0ea2db25dd45f7c12e75be5","tid":1650594,"uid":23672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:57:41.000Z","msg":"今晚真係一定要多人 跪求各位今晚點都要出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9603ce92d0763dac9dbdc427acc8c60129ad72f","tid":1650594,"uid":308154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:58:53.000Z","msg":"跪求大家出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10220a14aa9f4d99c893510e75cc9e51541d61b6","tid":1650594,"uid":194452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:13:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"